                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black">FIFO Queue</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-base-content/50">
                    The proper British queue. Exact arrival order. Deterministic. No cutting, no exceptions. <br/><br/>
                    Uses <code class="text-base-content/70">QueueAirlock</code>.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-secondary opacity-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100">
                    Try it
                    <svg class="h-4 w-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
                </div>
            </a>
