        </div>

        {# Architecture summary #}
        <div class="mt-12 rounded-3xl border border-base-300 bg-base-200 p-6 sm:p-8">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-base-content/40">Architecture</h3>
            <p class="mb-6 text-base-content/60">Every Airlock has three parts:</p>
            <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-4">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Seal</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-base-content/60">How capacity is enforced — lock, semaphore, or rate limiter</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-4">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">Admission Strategy</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-base-content/60">Who gets in next — FIFO, lottery, or backpressure</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-4">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">Notifier</p>
                    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-base-content/60">How waiters are told it's their turn — Mercure, WebSocket, polling</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
